{"word":"G3100 - μαθητεύω - mathēteúō - math-ayt-yoo'-o - Be disciple","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μαθητεύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">mathēteúō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">math-ayt-yoo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Be disciple</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"சீஷன், சீஷராக்குதல் - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"1. to be the disciple of one; to follow his precepts and instruction"},{"paragraph":"2. to make a disciple; to teach, instruct"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3101 - μαθητής - mathētḗs - math-ay-tes'/3101\">G3101</a>; intransitively to <i>become a pupil</i>; transitively to <i>disciple</i>, that is, enrol as scholar: - be disciple, instruct, teach.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2648/2648\">G2648</a>, <a href=\"#/G3100/3100\">G3100</a>, <a href=\"#/G3101/3101\">G3101</a>, <a href=\"#/G3102/3102\">G3102</a>, <a href=\"#/G3129/3129\">G3129</a>, <a href=\"#/G4827/4827\">G4827</a>"}]}